18
00:02:52,620 --> 00:02:55,260
You have to help make the same decision

19
00:02:55,860 --> 00:02:57,060
on several crucial things

20
00:02:57,260 --> 00:02:58,700
that decide Aranya's fate.

21
00:03:00,260 --> 00:03:02,060
This is the first one.

22
00:03:04,220 --> 00:03:05,940
When Junuo was executed that year,

23
00:03:06,380 --> 00:03:07,820
