24
00:03:08,580 --> 00:03:10,220
So you have to save her again this time,

25
00:03:10,580 --> 00:03:12,060
as Aranya did before.

26
00:03:12,700 --> 00:03:13,980
Besides, this is the key step for you

27
00:03:14,100 --> 00:03:16,100
to leave the Dream of Aranya.

28
00:03:21,500 --> 00:03:22,100
That's fine.

29
00:03:22,940 --> 00:03:24,060
Now that I have to do this,

30
00:03:24,340 --> 00:03:25,100
you should give me

31
00:03:25,100 --> 00:03:26,300
the same excuse as Aranya had at that time.

32
00:03:26,900 --> 00:03:28,620
Although she hadn't made as many troubles as I did,

33
00:03:29,060 --> 00:03:31,140
there was always a feud

34
00:03:31,260 --> 00:03:32,100
between Junuo and her.

35
00:03:32,260 --> 00:03:33,300
Why did she save Junuo

36
00:03:33,420 --> 00:03:34,900
at that crucial moment?

37
00:03:35,660 --> 00:03:36,940
Because the one she wanted to save at that time

38
00:03:37,940 --> 00:03:38,900
wasn't Junuo

39
00:03:39,820 --> 00:03:40,540
but Shen Ye.

40
00:03:40,860 --> 00:03:41,740
Shen Ye?

41
00:03:42,540 --> 00:03:43,620
What's the story?

42
00:03:44,420 --> 00:03:45,260
When Junuo was executed that day,

43
00:03:46,300 --> 00:03:47,980
Shen Ye came to save her.

44
00:03:48,940 --> 00:03:49,780
But he was in trouble unexpectedly.

45
00:03:50,500 --> 00:03:52,580
Aranya came out to save them both boldly.

46
00:03:53,980 --> 00:03:54,980
At that time, I thought

47
00:03:55,300 --> 00:03:57,660
there was enmity between her and Shen Ye,

48
00:03:58,620 --> 00:03:59,860
but I knew it later.

49
00:04:00,460 --> 00:04:01,540
Why she saved Shen Ye

50
00:04:02,620 --> 00:04:03,700
