Now that Aranya saved Shen Ye,

53
00:04:10,340 --> 00:04:12,380
did he know Aranya fell for him?

54
00:04:13,460 --> 00:04:16,860
The clan of inseparable king birds values chastity.

55
00:04:17,980 --> 00:04:19,900
Madam Qing Hua married twice,

56
00:04:20,460 --> 00:04:21,540
which Shen Ye disagreed.

57
00:04:22,660 --> 00:04:24,260
He couldn't fall for

58
00:04:24,380 --> 00:04:25,500
the two princesses who were given birth to by Madam Qing Hua

59
00:04:25,980 --> 00:04:26,940
after she remarried Xiangli Que,

60
00:04:27,540 --> 00:04:29,180
especially for Aranya.

61
00:04:31,140 --> 00:04:32,100
Among the three princesses,

62
00:04:32,900 --> 00:04:33,940
he could only

63
00:04:34,820 --> 00:04:35,980
fall for Junuo.

64
00:04:37,460 --> 00:04:39,220
But it's Aranya who saved him.

65
00:04:39,900 --> 00:04:41,620
He was supposed

66
00:04:41,740 --> 00:04:43,780
to requite Aranya for saving his life, wasn't he?

67
