75
00:05:02,980 --> 00:05:05,380
However, Aranya requested His Majesty

76
00:05:05,780 --> 00:05:06,620
to allow Shen Ye to live in her mansion

77
00:05:06,940 --> 00:05:08,700
and help her cast a sword

78
00:05:09,140 --> 00:05:10,100
in the name of Lord Xi Ze.

79
00:05:10,940 --> 00:05:11,580
Cast a sword?

80
00:05:14,660 --> 00:05:16,700
She used the excuse for presenting a sword
to the Crown Prince of the Sky Kingdom

81
00:05:16,860 --> 00:05:17,940
as a birthday gift

82
00:05:18,100 --> 00:05:19,700
to defend Shen Ye.

83
00:05:23,820 --> 00:05:24,700
But I'm afraid

84
00:05:25,500 --> 00:05:27,380
Shen Ye wouldn't have understood Aranya.

85
00:05:28,500 --> 00:05:29,380
From the perspective of him,

86
00:05:30,260 --> 00:05:31,940
that Aranya kept him in her mansion

87
00:05:32,820 --> 00:05:34,340
was merely to imprison him

88
00:05:35,060 --> 00:05:36,020
and take her revenge on him.

89
00:05:38,340 --> 00:05:40,660
Did Shen Ye return evil for good?

90
00:05:41,580 --> 00:05:43,060
Aranya shouldn't have been treated this way.

91
00:05:44,300 --> 00:05:46,860
I was always reminded of the words Aranya once said.

92
00:05:48,780 --> 00:05:50,980
"One has to follow his heart, his destiny and the situation,

93
00:05:52,100 --> 00:05:55,820
no matter who he is, an immortal or an ordinary person."

94
00:05:57,500 --> 00:05:58,180
It's a pity that

95
00:05:59,300 --> 00:06:01,500
Aranya fell for Shen Ye,

96
00:06:01,980 --> 00:06:03,020
but her destiny with Shen Ye

97
00:06:03,940 --> 00:06:05,300
was doomed in the situation.

98
00:06:10,340 --> 00:06:11,220
You mean,

99
00:06:11,820 --> 00:06:14,260
why did Aranya choose to be a good person?

100
00:06:14,860 --> 00:06:16,580
Why did she choose to suffer all this?

101
00:06:19,420 --> 00:06:21,580
If Aranya had acted as half open-minded as you,

102
00:06:22,660 --> 00:06:24,420
she wouldn't have ended up where she was.

103
00:06:27,620 --> 00:06:28,220
Since

104
00:06:29,180 --> 00:06:30,460
it's a big deal,

105
00:06:30,980 --> 00:06:32,140
you have to ponder over it.

106
00:06:38,140 --> 00:06:39,340
Something big is about to happen

107
00:06:40,540 --> 00:06:42,060
in the imperial palace tonight.

108
00:06:44,940 --> 00:06:45,940
Aren't you going to rise?

109
00:06:47,940 --> 00:06:51,140
I'm begging you to spare Junuo, Your Majesty.

110
00:06:52,580 --> 00:06:54,740
As the Elder Princess,

111
00:06:55,300 --> 00:06:57,580
Junuo committed adultery when she's unmarried.
And she also cheated the emperor.

112
00:06:58,060 --> 00:07:00,020
She should be guillotined according to the law.

113
00:07:01,060 --> 00:07:02,460
There's nothing I could do.

114
00:07:03,100 --> 00:07:03,780
Your Majesty,

115
00:07:05,140 --> 00:07:06,740
Junuo didn't make the mistake on purpose.

116
00:07:08,300 --> 00:07:09,580
Not on purpose?

117
00:07:11,420 --> 00:07:13,220
What she has done

118
00:07:13,340 --> 00:07:15,020
is a huge humiliation to the imperial family.

119
00:07:17,020 --> 00:07:18,980
If I don't guillotine her,

120
00:07:19,060 --> 00:07:21,620
everyone will consider that I abuse the law.

121
00:07:23,220 --> 00:07:25,820
No matter how unbearable I feel,

122
00:07:27,220 --> 00:07:28,380
I have to do it.

123
00:07:29,460 --> 00:07:31,500
If you really wanted to spare Junuo

124
00:07:33,460 --> 00:07:35,380
how come you used these words as an excuse?

125
00:07:40,500 --> 00:07:42,180
Do you know what you're saying?

126
00:07:43,380 --> 00:07:44,020
Your Majesty,

127
00:07:46,220 --> 00:07:47,740
after all these years,

128
00:07:49,900 --> 00:07:51,700
you still can't bear Junuo, can you?

129
00:07:58,780 --> 00:08:00,140
If I didn't bear Junuo,

130
00:08:00,540 --> 00:08:01,780
I wouldn't have waited till today.

131
00:08:05,060 --> 00:08:05,860
It's you

132
00:08:07,060 --> 00:08:09,060
who always cover up for her and connive what she does.

133
00:08:10,980 --> 00:08:13,300
I won't blame you for that.

134
00:08:15,820 --> 00:08:16,820
Don't mention

135
00:08:17,140 --> 00:08:18,260
releasing Junuo anymore.

136
00:08:30,180 --> 00:08:30,980
What are you saying?

137
00:08:31,300 --> 00:08:32,100
Say it again.

138
00:08:32,460 --> 00:08:33,420
The day Junuo was executed,

139
00:08:33,980 --> 00:08:35,940
Aranya flew to the guillotine

140
00:08:36,580 --> 00:08:38,620
with a naked blade, and she sacrificed her blood to the sword,

141
00:08:39,140 --> 00:08:40,660
which finally saved both of them.

142
00:08:41,420 --> 00:08:42,300
Why did she have to save them

143
00:08:42,460 --> 00:08:43,980
by sacrificing her blood to the guillotine?

144
00:08:45,420 --> 00:08:47,340
What Junuo did was ignominious,

145
00:08:47,780 --> 00:08:49,740
but the execution of a princess

146
00:08:49,980 --> 00:08:51,140
should be recorded in the annals of history.

147
00:08:51,740 --> 00:08:52,860
So they made an elaborate plan.

148
00:08:54,100 --> 00:08:56,220
Only clan relatives of the imperial family
were allowed to watch the execution.

149
00:08:56,700 --> 00:08:59,020
The Lingshu Stage, in front of the immortal palace,
was chosen to be the place of execution.

150
00:08:59,460 --> 00:09:00,420
The executioner must be extraordinary,

151
00:09:01,060 --> 00:09:04,060
since he was chosen from those

152
00:09:04,500 --> 00:09:05,900
whose families had been hangmen for more than three generations.

153
00:09:06,460 --> 00:09:07,500
There are so many traditions

154
00:09:07,660 --> 00:09:08,980
for the beheading of the inseparable king birds.

155
00:09:11,220 --> 00:09:13,260
The most important one is the sword,

156
00:09:14,260 --> 00:09:15,580
which is the sacred treasure of the inseparable king birds.

157
00:09:15,900 --> 00:09:16,620
White Tiger Sword.

158
00:09:17,500 --> 00:09:18,340
White Tiger Sword?

159
00:09:19,660 --> 00:09:20,460
White Tiger Sword

160
00:09:21,180 --> 00:09:23,540
should be sacrificed by the wrist blood of the one
who's about to be executed before use

161
00:09:24,220 --> 00:09:26,220
in order to release the double-winged white-fronted tiger
that protects the sword.

162
00:09:26,740 --> 00:09:28,420
The double-winged white-fronted tiger will

163
00:09:28,540 --> 00:09:30,220
swallow the flesh and blood as well as
the primordial spirit of the one who is about to be executed,

164
00:09:30,740 --> 00:09:33,620
and trap the primordial spirit in the sword
to make the one executed incapable of going to heaven.

165
00:09:34,740 --> 00:09:35,780
It's too horrible.

166
00:09:36,180 --> 00:09:38,700
Since the white-fronted tiger is so fierce,

167
00:09:38,820 --> 00:09:40,300
how can I withstand it?

168
00:09:41,860 --> 00:09:42,820
Don't be flustered in advance.

169
00:09:43,780 --> 00:09:44,660
I'm about to tell you

170
00:09:44,860 --> 00:09:47,540
the key to seal the tiger back to the sword.

171
00:09:49,140 --> 00:09:50,220
The white-fronted tiger is eager for blood.

172
00:09:50,580 --> 00:09:52,500
As long as you volunteer to feed it with fresh blood,

173
00:09:52,900 --> 00:09:54,780
and seal it back to the sword with your spiritual power,

174
00:09:55,420 --> 00:09:57,620
you'll be able to save Shen Ye and Junuo.

175
00:09:58,380 --> 00:10:00,340
Will I have to feed it with fresh blood?

176
00:10:01,140 --> 00:10:02,540
The blood isn't yours anyhow.

177
00:10:02,740 --> 00:10:03,700
It's Aranya's blood.

178
00:10:04,020 --> 00:10:04,660
What are you scared of?

179
00:10:05,740 --> 00:10:06,660
You're telling the truth,

180
00:10:07,020 --> 00:10:08,780
but I'm the one who is about to suffer the pain.

181
00:10:09,620 --> 00:10:11,340
What a daredevil Aranya is!

182
00:10:11,980 --> 00:10:13,140
I'm afraid of pain most.

183
00:10:55,740 --> 00:10:56,380
Shen Ye.

184
00:11:17,020 --> 00:11:19,180
She betrayed you, but you still want to save her?

185
00:11:20,140 --> 00:11:21,260
We grew up together,

186
00:11:21,700 --> 00:11:23,580
even she did something wrong.
If there is a chance for her to be alive,

187
00:11:23,740 --> 00:11:24,780
how could I not save her?

188
00:11:25,340 --> 00:11:26,220
What a big speech you make!

189
00:11:29,700 --> 00:11:30,780
Do you still remember me?

190
00:11:32,220 --> 00:11:32,860
I do.

191
00:11:34,020 --> 00:11:35,180
You're Xiangli Aranya.

192
00:11:46,780 --> 00:11:48,740
I guess you haven't come up with the way

193
00:11:48,900 --> 00:11:49,940
to seal the white-fronted tiger back.

194
00:12:00,540 --> 00:12:02,100
People say that the blood of Your Excellency

195
00:12:02,260 --> 00:12:03,500
can purify the dirty.

196
00:12:04,060 --> 00:12:04,900
So I'm wondering whether or not

197
00:12:05,060 --> 00:12:07,020
Your Excellency will show mercy

198
00:12:07,500 --> 00:12:08,900
and purify my blood today.

199
00:12:52,900 --> 00:12:53,540
Aranya,

200
00:12:56,540 --> 00:12:58,500
the day that Junuo is about to be executed is coming.

201
00:12:59,380 --> 00:13:03,340
Qing Hua will come to discuss the strategy with me soon.

202
00:13:05,660 --> 00:13:06,740
But I have no idea

203
00:13:07,540 --> 00:13:08,340
whether now you will do the same

204
00:13:11,860 --> 00:13:14,260
as you used to that year.

205
00:13:25,060 --> 00:13:25,900
Your Excellency.

206
00:13:31,580 --> 00:13:32,100
Come in.

207
00:13:35,100 --> 00:13:36,980
Your Excellency, Her Majesty is coming to see you.

208
00:13:42,860 --> 00:13:43,900
Welcome her in.

209
00:13:44,380 --> 00:13:44,820
Yes.

210
00:14:01,260 --> 00:14:02,100
Archmage.

211
00:14:03,740 --> 00:14:04,860
What do you

212
00:14:05,380 --> 00:14:06,420
come for this time?

213
00:14:20,900 --> 00:14:23,580
You must have known what happened to Junuo.

214
00:14:24,500 --> 00:14:25,700
I know you used to

215
00:14:26,020 --> 00:14:28,340
be indifferent to what happened to the imperial family,

216
00:14:30,140 --> 00:14:31,940
but there's an engagement between Junuo and you.

217
00:14:32,700 --> 00:14:34,060
Will you be indifferent to her either?

218
00:14:37,620 --> 00:14:38,820
The evidence is irrefutable,

219
00:14:39,700 --> 00:14:41,260
and the sentence is made totally based on the law.

220
00:14:41,580 --> 00:14:43,260
Junuo truly did something wrong, and she should be punished,

221
00:14:43,820 --> 00:14:45,660
but you also have the right to make the decision,

222
00:14:46,660 --> 00:14:48,860
How could Xiangli Que make the decision on his own

223
00:14:49,100 --> 00:14:50,620
without discussing with you?

224
00:14:53,780 --> 00:14:55,020
Princess fornicated her master,

225
00:14:55,860 --> 00:14:56,860
and she was guilty as charged.

226
00:14:58,380 --> 00:14:59,780
I wouldn't have been able to change anything,
even if I had been present.

227
00:15:00,340 --> 00:15:01,300
That His Majesty made the decision without me

228
00:15:02,180 --> 00:15:03,500
was to protect my fame.

229
00:15:07,620 --> 00:15:08,140
Indeed,

230
00:15:09,540 --> 00:15:10,620
Junuo is guilty to you,

231
00:15:11,260 --> 00:15:14,060
since she's your wife-to-be.

232
00:15:16,300 --> 00:15:18,140
Anyway, Junuo is also your cousin.

233
00:15:20,060 --> 00:15:21,140
As the Archmage,

234
00:15:22,060 --> 00:15:23,580
you must have some way to save her.

235
00:15:34,460 --> 00:15:35,180
Shen Ye,

236
00:15:36,380 --> 00:15:37,100
Junuo is the only descendant

237
00:15:37,220 --> 00:15:38,740
left by my late husband to me.

238
00:15:39,540 --> 00:15:41,460
Do you really want to see her

239
00:15:41,860 --> 00:15:43,300
killed by the White Tiger Sword?

240
00:15:46,820 --> 00:15:49,860
Please save Junuo for the sake of my late husband.

241
00:15:51,020 --> 00:15:52,660
I'm begging you, please.

242
00:16:43,660 --> 00:16:44,140
Master.

243
00:17:03,460 --> 00:17:04,180
Are you hurt?

244
00:17:04,700 --> 00:17:06,620
Shall I find a pharmacist to heal you?

245
00:17:07,060 --> 00:17:08,580
I'm fine. Don't bother.

246
00:17:10,380 --> 00:17:13,940
I used to think that you pled illness to live in solitude
and transferred the position to me

247
00:17:14,500 --> 00:17:15,900
was because you didn't want
to take care of business in the immortal palace.

248
00:17:16,220 --> 00:17:17,380
You wanted to be free.

249
00:17:18,380 --> 00:17:20,020
I didn't expect that you're hurt.

250
00:17:20,660 --> 00:17:21,540
What did you

251
00:17:22,220 --> 00:17:23,300
come to me for just now?

252
00:17:25,740 --> 00:17:26,620
You don't come to me

253
00:17:27,420 --> 00:17:28,940
to talk about this, do you?

254
00:17:30,940 --> 00:17:31,460
No.

255
00:17:33,620 --> 00:17:34,740
You have seen that

256
00:17:35,660 --> 00:17:36,780
Her Majesty came to me.

257
00:17:38,380 --> 00:17:39,260
She wanted to know

258
00:17:40,340 --> 00:17:41,620
whether I could save Junuo.

259
00:17:42,700 --> 00:17:44,420
Junuo is your wife-to-be.

260
00:17:45,100 --> 00:17:46,060
Now that it has happened,

261
00:17:46,540 --> 00:17:48,700
whether to save her or not, it's your own decision to make.

262
00:17:49,220 --> 00:17:50,100
It's none of my business.

263
00:17:53,060 --> 00:17:53,980
You go back first.

264
00:17:54,860 --> 00:17:55,980
I need some rest.

265
00:18:17,540 --> 00:18:20,140
There are so many odds in the dream world.

266
00:18:21,100 --> 00:18:22,020
Aranya changes,

267
00:18:22,580 --> 00:18:24,020
and the Junuo thing happens ahead of schedule.

268
00:18:24,780 --> 00:18:27,460
Lord Xi Ze seems to be different from what he used to.

269
00:18:28,860 --> 00:18:30,140
Junuo is about to be executed in a few days.

270
00:18:30,820 --> 00:18:33,740
What on earth is going to happen?

271
00:18:51,340 --> 00:18:54,140
There's only one day ahead of the execution of Junuo.

272
00:18:56,100 --> 00:18:57,740
I still don't know how well Fengjiu can shoot arrows.

